\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1.3}{\ignorespaces Four different commercial and defense eVTOL aircraft in various stages of development and use. Each design is specialized to the use case and developer's design philosophy. Figures \ref {fig:archer} and \ref {fig:BetaTech} are commercial eVTOL air taxis in development from Archer Aviation and Beta Technologies respectively. The V-22 Osprey in Figure \ref {fig:osprey} is a famous VTOL that has seen extensive development and deployment for the U.S. Military. Figure \ref {fig:zipline} is the Zipline VTOL, which is under development for food and package delivery.}}{4}{figure.caption.7}%
