\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2.6}{\ignorespaces Plots of takeoff shape. Path found using scaled function of $d = -\sqrt {n}$. The control points, shown in subfigure \ref {fig:TakeoffShapeWithControl}, are spaced increasingly far apart to simulate increasing velocity.}}{23}{figure.caption.14}%
