\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {5.23}{\ignorespaces Zoom in on SFC connection. Comparison of three B-Spline outputs at boundaries. Green is minimum distance, yellow is minimum velocity, and orange is minimum acceleration.}}{76}{figure.caption.59}%
